title: NyNy Coffee & Bakery v1.1
description:
Join NyNy for another exciting experience serving delicious pastry and hot coffee.
NyNy needs your help serving the customers their desired orders on time.

The game includes:

- Unlimited levels of fast paced customer-serving fun.
- Upgrade your shop express with up to 16 items to sell.
- Performance items are available for even faster play.
- Cute characters and graphics.
- For a more challenging experience, pastry run out fast, so you need to continuously make more pastry.
- Extend your play time by buying heart shaped donuts from the shop section using money earned in the game.
- Share your scores, achievements, and compete with your friends online using Openfeint.

What's in this version:
Bug fixing
